Download Flutter SDK, unzip it to a location (prefer the path without space)
navigate to flutter > Run flutter_console windows batch file. If successull. copy path of flutter > bin and add it to environmental
variable path
Execute 'flutter' command from CMD.



Android Studio is required. (for Android Dev)
XCode for iOS Dev.

download and install visual studio code
and then install extension flutter
copy this url to marketplace in VS Code : https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=Dart-Code.flutter

Commands:
-----------------------------------------------------------------
Check installation        flutter doctor
accept android licenses   flutter doctor --android-licenses
Create App:               flutter create AppName
clean the cache:          flutter clean       //from project root dir

